longBusinessSummary: Tinkerine Studios Ltd. designs, produces, and distributes 3D printers, software, and related online educational content in Canada, and the United States. The company offers DittoPro 3D printer; Tinkerine Suite, a 3D slicing software; PLA filaments; personal protective equipment; and 3D printing accessories. It also sells its products online. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Delta, Canada.
